band.urls module

band.urls.urlpatterns = [<URLPattern 'welcome/' [name='welcome']>, <URLPattern 'about/' [name='about']>, <URLPattern 'contact/' [name='contact']>, <URLPattern 'songs/' [name='song_list']>]

URL configuration for the band app.

Defines URL patterns for various pages of the band app, including the welcome page, about page, contact page, and song list page.

band.urls.app_name

The namespace for the band app URLs.

Type:

str

URL Patterns:

  • /welcome/: URL pattern for the welcome page.

  • /about/: URL pattern for the about page.

  • /contact/: URL pattern for the contact page.

  • /songs/: URL pattern for the song list page.

Each URL pattern is assigned to its corresponding view function.

band.views module

This module contains view functions for rendering various pages of the website.

The views include: - Welcome page - About Us page - Contact details page - List of songs
